data.title: 2007) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Joan Crum, 73, passed on Sunday, February 18, 2007 at Sunrise Assisted Living in Fort Wayne.   Born in Jay County, IN, she was a homemaker and also worked at GE for a number of years. Joan was a loving mother and grandmother, and enjoyed cooking, sewing, fishing and especially community service.   Survivors include...
